{"tid":1659390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月17日11:30 香港專業教育學院黃克兢分校要人","createTime":"2019-10-17T02:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T06:49:33.000Z","uid":144718,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c2339f9da994d2512ababd83a12dd1af72062fa6","tid":1659390,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"我們只有幾個訴求<br />\n<br />\n  第一，要求VTC釋出完整CCTV片段。<br />\n  第二 ，要求VTC就多次隱瞞及欺騙同學作出解釋。<br />\n  第三 ，要求院方解釋為何昨天HKDI釋出不完整的CCTV片段後反口不再為10月15日答應我們以院方名義向HKDI作出任何遣責。<br />\n  第四，要求院方以香港專業教育學院黃克兢分校名義就上述第一及第二項訴求向HKDI施壓，否則將會視院方與HKDI同流合污、包庇殺人。<br />\n  <br />\n  最後請院方慎重考慮，若然在10月17日下午15:00尚未得到院方作出滿意答覆，黃克兢學生不排除。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動升級</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"3881d067c451e6caad410cd22dbb86354ebb3118","tid":1659390,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ca65f2482393511881321abca7650512cc649659","tid":1659390,"uid":215102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aced56e68c1f3c1502dc5d719735f6e83bfb849","tid":1659390,"uid":215102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"564ed83ec7e753642afe5275dd2f4c4da4b5b56d","tid":1659390,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"b2616bc1e7e53562383c9598993ebdd40f48deba","tid":1659390,"uid":215102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9953dd3c4afcb4bc9077dde295ba6c42f5da18f0","tid":1659390,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:25:3